name: Somos Nosotros
description:
Sad Blu- Somos Nosotros (Prod by. Blu)
This song was created on April 4, 2020, during the COVID-19 global pandemic. This event allowed me to find the time to take my musical productions to the next level and begin to find my voice and my style. Somos Nosotros is a musical fusion between Brazilian Funk and Trap. 

Artist- Sad Blu 
Producer- Sad Blu 
Cover Art- Sad Blu
